title: Ep44 Gossip at the Corpse Cart
description:
This month's GACC serves up gooey delights in the form of booger salads, hot dog filler, dog barf, and a tanning bed mess, plus a recycling center disappearance, abandoned guinea pigs, and a very weird way to die. Tune in for this month's Gossip at the Corpse Cart!

For a full list of show sponsors, visit https://wineandcrimepodcast.com/sponsors/
